 🎓 CGPA Calculator in C++

This is a simple yet practical C++ program that calculates a student CGPA based on their letter grades and credit hours. It demonstrates core programming concepts like arrays, loops, conditionals, and formatted output.

 💡 Features

- Accepts up to 50 courses
- Supports letter grades (A+, A, B-, etc.) with case-insensitive input
- Maps grades to GPA values using a standard scale
- Calculates total grade points and final CGPA
- Displays a formatted summary table of all courses

 📊 Grading Scale

| Grade | Range       | GPA Value |
|-------|-------------|-----------|
| A+    | 90+         | 4.0       |
| A-    | 85–89       | 3.7       |
| A     | 80–84       | 3.5       |
| B+    | 75–79       | 3.3       |
| B     | 70–74       | 3.0       |
| B-    | 65–69       | 2.7       |
| C+    | 60–64       | 2.3       |
| C     | 55–59       | 2.0       |
| D     | 40–54       | 1.0       |
| F     | Below 33    | 0.0       |

